Package net.minecraftforge.client.model

Interface IModelBuilder<T extends IModelBuilder<T>>

All Known Implementing Classes:
IModelBuilder.Collecting, IModelBuilder.Simple
@Deprecated(forRemoval=true, since="1.21.5") public interface IModelBuilder<T extends IModelBuilder<T>>
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
Use QuadCollection instead.
Base interface for any object that collects culled and unculled faces and bakes them into a model.

Provides a generic base implementation via of(boolean, boolean, boolean, ItemTransforms, TextureAtlasSprite, RenderTypeGroup, RenderTypeGroup) and a quad-collecting alternative via collecting(List).
